{%- comment -%}
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PRODUCT VARIANTS CARD (新版 product variants)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

以卡片网格展示一组关联产品（PC 端一行两个，H5 端一行一个）。当前正在浏览的产品卡片会带黑色边框。
卡片之间通过 <a> 链接互相跳转（与既有 product_variations 一致，无需 JS）。

价格规则：
* 展示价格为「折扣后价格」= variant.price - custom.discount_money_count
* Save 金额取 custom.discount_money_count
* custom.discount_money_count 是「金额(money)」类型字段，其 .value 在数值运算中即为最小货币单位(分)，
  因此 times: 1 仅做数值强制转换，无需再乘以 100（与 price_second / discount_code 写法保持一致）。

配置来源：
* 标题(Heading)         : 固定写死为 "Choice"
* 关联产品列表(Products): current_product.metafields.custom.variants_card_products （产品参考列表，需包含当前产品自身）
* 卡片内的产品标题      : 每个产品自身的 metafields.custom.variants_card_title    （单行文本，留空回退到产品标题）
* Save 金额 / 折扣      : 每个产品自身的 metafields.custom.discount_money_count    （金额，已有字段）

********************************************
Supported variables
********************************************

* current_product: 当前页面正在浏览的产品
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign pvc_heading = 'Choice'
  assign pvc_products = current_product.metafields.custom.variants_card_products.value
-%}

<style>
  .product-variants-card__heading {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-block-end: 1rem;
    color: rgb(var(--text-color));
  }

  .product-variants-card__list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 1000px) {
    .product-variants-card__list {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  .product-variants-card__item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto minmax(0, 1fr);
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgb(var(--text-color) / 0.12);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgb(var(--background));
    color: rgb(var(--text-color));
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .product-variants-card__item:hover {
    border-color: rgb(var(--text-color) / 0.35);
  }

  /* 当前正在浏览的产品：黑色加粗边框。padding 减 1px 抵消加粗的边框，避免卡片尺寸跳动 */
  .product-variants-card__item.is-selected {
    border-color: rgb(var(--text-color));
    border-width: 2px;
    padding: calc(1rem - 1px);
  }

  .product-variants-card__media {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .product-variants-card__image {
    max-width: 100%;
    max-height: 100%;
    width: auto;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .product-variants-card__info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.15rem;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .product-variants-card__title {
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .product-variants-card__price {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .product-variants-card__save {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: rgb(var(--text-color) / 0.6);
  }
</style>

<div class="product-variants-card">
  {%- if pvc_heading != blank -%}
    <p class="product-variants-card__heading">{{ pvc_heading | escape }}</p>
  {%- endif -%}

  <div class="product-variants-card__list">
    {%- for variation in pvc_products -%}
      {%- liquid
        assign variation_variant = variation.selected_or_first_available_variant

        assign pvc_save_cents = 0
        assign pvc_discount_value = variation.metafields.custom.discount_money_count.value
        if pvc_discount_value != blank and pvc_discount_value > 0
          assign pvc_save_cents = pvc_discount_value | times: 1
        endif
        assign pvc_price_cents = variation_variant.price | minus: pvc_save_cents

        assign pvc_title = variation.metafields.custom.variants_card_title
        if pvc_title == blank
          assign pvc_title = variation.title
        endif

        assign pvc_is_selected = false
        if variation.id == current_product.id
          assign pvc_is_selected = true
        endif
      -%}

      <a href="{{ variation.url }}" class="product-variants-card__item{% if pvc_is_selected %} is-selected{% endif %}"{% if pvc_is_selected %} aria-current="true"{% endif %}>
        <div class="product-variants-card__media">
          {%- if variation.featured_media != blank -%}
            {{- variation.featured_media | image_url: width: 144 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy', sizes: '72px', widths: '72,144', class: 'product-variants-card__image' -}}
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>

        <div class="product-variants-card__info">
          <span class="product-variants-card__title">{{ pvc_title | escape }}</span>
          <span class="product-variants-card__price">{{ pvc_price_cents | money }}</span>
          {%- if pvc_save_cents > 0 -%}
            <span class="product-variants-card__save">Save {{ pvc_save_cents | money }} with Coupon</span>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      </a>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</div>
